@page "/about"

<PageTitle>About</PageTitle>

<h1>Architecture</h1>
<pre class="bg-light p-3 rounded">
Blazor UI  (this app, port 5xxx)
    │  HTTP
    ▼
python_engine_api.py  (:8765)
    │
    ▼
gui/review_app/pipeline_api.py
    │
    ▼
renderer/engine.py  +  gen_jobs  (Grok, ffmpeg, projects/*)
</pre>
<p>
    Stage 1/2 plans and <code>scenes.json</code> stay in each project folder.
    This UI only <strong>starts</strong> work and shows job status.
    Full Adaptation / Characters / clip review can move here over time;
    Streamlit remains available for deep review.
</p>
